    "1201602": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Ei",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Ei",
                    "T": "Oh, is this the marketplace? It's a far cry from how I remember it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ei",
                    "T": "The stores have changed, and so have the vendors... well, that's to be expected."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ogura Mio",
                    "T": "It's... the Shogun!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rie",
                    "T": "What is the Almighty Shogun doing here?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mikoshi Genichirou",
                    "T": "Isn't the Shogun sick? This is quite sudden..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ei",
                    "T": "I appear to have frightened the people."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Well, what did you expect? The Almighty Shogun makes an impromptu appearance in town. People are gonna freak out a bit."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It seems like a bit of an overreaction."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Doesn't the Shogun normally patrol these parts?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ei",
                    "T": "Patrolling the streets is the Tenryou Commission's job. The Shogun has a lot of information to process and orders to give out. She doesn't have time to deal with it herself."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ei",
                    "T": "Additionally, the Shogun has no need of recreation. There would be no need for her to come here just to pass the time or to relax."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So what do we do now? Should we go away for a while and make a more low-profile return later?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ei",
                    "T": "Why? It's not like I'm here to cause trouble. Let's just relax."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "It was more the ordinary people that Paimon was worried about..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Never mind. This definitely seems like your style, Ei."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
