    "1201606": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Tomoki",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Tomoki",
                    "T": "Sh—Shogun, I... excuse me..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ei",
                    "T": "It's alright, relax. I'm just here to look around. I'm having a change of pace today."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ei",
                    "T": "Could you tell me about the items you are selling?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tomoki",
                    "T": "Of course! I've got all kinds of snacks here: Takoyaki, Dango... and, uh, Milk and so on."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh? Milk? Sounds kinda like the odd one out..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tomoki",
                    "T": "It might sound odd, but it is in fact my specialty."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tomoki",
                    "T": "You see, many of the stores in town are already very well established. I couldn't compete with them no matter what I sell."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tomoki",
                    "T": "So my idea was to create some new combinations to give customers a novel experience."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tomoki",
                    "T": "For example, my latest concoction is this Dango Milk. When the Dango are worked into a viscous form, they mix very nicely with the milk."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tomoki",
                    "T": "The focus is not just the taste, but also the unique texture."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ei",
                    "T": "Dango with Milk... hmm, I've never heard of it. What made you want to do this?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tomoki",
                    "T": "Ah, I'm sorry, Shogun! I've got no bone to pick with eternity!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ei",
                    "T": "I said relax, there's no need to go treading on eggshells. Do you really think the Eternity I pursue is something that can be shaken by Dango and Milk?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tomoki",
                    "T": "(Huh? Why do I feel like... she's different than I expected?)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tomoki",
                    "T": "Actually, it came to me by chance. A friend was catering once and made too many Dango, so they gave some to me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tomoki",
                    "T": "But there were more than I had use for. My Milk wasn't selling well at that time either, and both Dango and Milk have a short shelf life..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tomoki",
                    "T": "So I thought I'd try mixing the two as I had nothing to lose. To my surprise, in the right proportion, it tasted superb."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ei",
                    "T": "A chance combination. Hmm, interesting. May I try this drink?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tomoki",
                    "T": "The Almighty Shogun wants to try!? Well, certainly! And you two should try it, too!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ei",
                    "T": "Nice, it's sweet. The sensation is not so different from eating a dessert. A unique beverage indeed."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yeah. It's definitely a drink, but it also feels like eating food."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ei",
                    "T": "It's a little bit like... porridge? But the resemblance is only superficial..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ei",
                    "T": "Anyway. I like it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tomoki",
                    "T": "I'm very glad you approve!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ei",
                    "T": "I imagine that an item as delicious as this Dango Milk must sell exceptionally well, no?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tomoki",
                    "T": "Heh, well... I won't lie to you. Sales are very average."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ei",
                    "T": "Huh. So it's selling slowly? Why is that?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tomoki",
                    "T": "Because... most people aren't willing to give it a try. They think it's an unusual combination. Even though everyone who's tried it before rates it highly..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tomoki",
                    "T": "...I'm not saying the Almighty Shogun has unusual tastes! Please don't take it the wrong way!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ei",
                    "T": "Ah, I see. Well, that can be fixed. I'll just have the Yashiro Commission order a few hundred cups and go door-to-door delivering them."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tomoki",
                    "T": "No, no, no, Almighty Shogun, that's too much!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ei",
                    "T": "Is it? I just want them to try it. It would be a shame for them to miss out on Dango Milk."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tomoki",
                    "T": "I, uh... haha."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "So you like sweet things?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ei",
                    "T": "Of course. I've heard that most humans like desserts, so it's not unusual that I should enjoy them too. Miko agrees with me on this."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Do you want another cup?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ei",
                    "T": "Ooh, I would love... N—No, no need. That would be needlessly indulgent."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ei",
                    "T": "Ahhhh. There's nothing like dessert for improving one's mood. Much more enjoyable than meditating alone all the time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ei",
                    "T": "By the way, Miko mentioned that she founded something called the Yae Publishing House to sell some sort of... light novels."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ei",
                    "T": "She's always bragging to me about it, but it's difficult for me to really imagine without seeing the place for myself. Can you take me there?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Sure. Let's go and have a look."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
